text.tspan: Within a defined genomic window, prioritize potentially
informative reads that overlap with common SNPs
Randomly resample reads and compute likelihoods of
observed alleles under competing ploidy hypotheses
Classify ploidy state of the genomic interval
Compare with likelihood ratio and repeat step C multiple
times to form a bootstrap distribution
Repeat steps A - D in consecutive genomic windows and
sum log likelihood ratios over larger genomic intervals
